General.Name: Fuse Group Holding Inc
General.Description: Fuse Group Holding Inc. offers consulting services to mining industry clients to find acquisition targets in the United States and internationally. It primarily focuses on the mining and biotech areas. The company was formerly known as Fuse Enterprises Inc. and changed its name to Fuse Group Holding Inc. in May 2019. Fuse Group Holding Inc. was incorporated in 2013 and is headquartered in Arcadia, California.
